data.description: Presenting a meticulously maintained 3BR/2.5BA home in the acclaimed Richland 2 School District. Nestled near I-77, I-20, Fort Jackson, and Sandhills Shopping Center, this residence offers convenience and accessibility. Enjoy a 1-car garage, a beautifully designed kitchen with granite countertops, and a spacious main-floor master suite with a sizable closet and ensuite bath featuring a separate shower and tub. The stunning vaulted ceilings add a touch of elegance. Experience a seamless blend of a modern floor plan and timeless design. Don't miss this opportunity to make this exceptional property your forever home. Schedule your viewing today!
